text:
Shelter Baptist Church is at 26 Sin Ming Lane. #06-113 Midview City.
You can take 410W to Sin Ming Ave from bishan bus interchange, 8 bus-stop to B08 Bus stop at Ai Tong school and walk into BrightHill Lane at 15 mins brisk walking the the rear of 26 Midview City.
Less then 1000 members.
Worship for English, chinese and Sunday schools at 10am to 11.30am.
Good place to exercise n gym.
